<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>[سورة الضحى <span class="c2">(٩٣)</span> : الآيات ٧ الى ٩]<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَوَجَدَكَ ضَالاًّ فَهَدى <span class="c2">(٧)</span> وَوَجَدَكَ عائِلاً فَأَغْنى <span class="c2">(٨)</span> فَأَمَّا الْيَتِيمَ فَلا تَقْهَرْ <span class="c2">(٩)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٧-<span class="c5"> وَوَجَدَكَ ضَالًّا فَهَدى:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَوَجَدَكَ ضَالًّا حائرا لا تنفعك المعتقدات حولك.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَهَدى فهداك إلى منهج الحق.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٨-<span class="c5"> وَوَجَدَكَ عائِلًا فَأَغْنى:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَوَجَدَكَ عائِلًا ووجدك فقيرا من المال.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَأَغْنى فأغناك بما أعطاك من رزق.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٩-<span class="c5"> فَأَمَّا الْيَتِيمَ فَلا تَقْهَرْ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>فَلا تَقْهَرْ فلا تذله.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>[سورة الضحى <span class="c2">(٩٣)</span> : الآيات ١٠ الى ١١]<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَأَمَّا السَّائِلَ فَلا تَنْهَرْ <span class="c2">(١٠)</span> وَأَمَّا بِنِعْمَةِ رَبِّكَ فَحَدِّثْ <span class="c2">(١١)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>١٠-<span class="c5"> وَأَمَّا السَّائِلَ فَلا تَنْهَرْ:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>فَلا تَنْهَرْ فلا ترده بقسوة.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>١١-<span class="c5"> وَأَمَّا بِنِعْمَةِ رَبِّكَ فَحَدِّثْ:</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>فَحَدِّثْ شكرا لله وإظهارا للنعمة.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>